---
title: Maple Sausage Breakfast Sandwiches Serves 2 | with Cheddar Cheese and Fried Eggs
description: The answer to your lazy Sunday morning routine! These breakfast sammies come together in a flash, so that you can sink your teeth into cheesy, salty-sweet goodness that much faster. A fresh chopped fruit salad makes for the perfect side to complete this five-star brunch.
